title: Kennet River (New Zealand)
text: The Kennet River is a river of the northeast of <a href="New%20Zealand">New Zealand</a>'s <a href="South%20Island">South Island</a>. It flows northwest of <a href="Molesworth%20Station">Molesworth Station</a>s south, joining the upper <a href="Awatere%20River">Awatere River</a>.
